<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_106_r2l1">Mathes von Mengoſreẅt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_106_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Mathes als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ıſt vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l3">ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> niht füklıch . <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglolfſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> ıchts ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l4">ſache gen Jm <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt . Vnd als Jr ſchreıbt wıe <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> frıcʒ . <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l5"><expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> hab . vnd Jn ſchuldıg daʒ er Jn gen vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>raten</expan> ſölt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . da tut er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l6">Jm vnrecht vnd <expan>vngutl<ex>ich</ex></expan> an . vnd wa des rede an vns kombt . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jn dar - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_106_r2l7">Jnn <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> als wır das mıt warheıt wol tun <expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_106" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Mathes von Mengosrewt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Mathes, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu ist uns zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht füklich,
                                <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> vom
                            <expan>Eglolfst<ex>ein</ex></expan> ichts zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> sache gen im
                            <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> ist. Und als ir schreibt, wie
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Fricz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> Burkart <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> hab
                        und in schuldig, daz er in gen uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>raten</expan> sölt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, da tut er im unrecht und
                                <expan>ungutl<ex>ich</ex></expan> an, und wa des rede an uns kombt,
                        so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in darinn <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en,</ex></expan> als wir das mit warheit wol
                        tun <expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
